slike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:19:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70438f583c6fbc97e4d197acf4a281d76276ce1d","tid":1618813,"uid":109437,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:23:02.000Z","msg":"五大訴求又變番五個都冇解決過了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff3e4ec2842fceb5e36e63dbc0437bd65729942","tid":1618813,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:23:46.000Z","msg":"立法會已失效"},{"pid":"66398f625ec4144841e40ab26e73080136fb5670","tid":1618813,"uid":306259,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"cbdc216e372d271bf5c702abc6fbf2155148b7df","tid":1618813,"uid":160766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:36:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">四分鐘睇晒點解《禁蒙面法》同《緊急法》有咩關係！</span></strong></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b8AH5yZJidA&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Db8AH5yZJidA%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3kPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=01d81f25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b8AH5yZJidA&amp;feature=youtu.be</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">蒙面法只係前菜！好戲就係緊急法！！兩樣嘢息息相關！</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">繞過立法會立法，政府唔會再遵從法律程序處理法律問題，仲講乜法治！！！</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>推晒比所有人睇懶人包！！！！</strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全力反對「蒙面法」！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:27:42.000Z","msg":"【將恐懼變成革命嘅契機】<br />\n緊急法實行在即，人心惶惶係必然，但千祈唔好畀恐懼控制我哋。越係恐懼，就越要無畏，越要冷靜思考。<br />\n<br />\n至於大家一聽到禁蒙面法，都不期然諗起梁天琦三年前嘅嗰番說話&mdash;&mdash;烏克蘭革命誕生於惡法嘅施行。 今日香港政權跟隨烏克蘭政權嘅手段，搏嘅係香港人唔敢好似烏克蘭人咁反抗，只敢「遊行」、「集會」，不敢明言「革命」。<br />\n<br />\n歷史上有惡法促成革命嘅例子，但不代表我哋翹埋雙手革命就會發生。本channel名為《香港革命指南》，就係要大家意識到呢場唔係「運動」、「示威」，而係香港人顛覆極權嘅真正革命。<br />\n<br />\n政權再次向我哋宣戰。香港人，你哋準備好未？<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We are against the police state<br />\n我哋正與警察國家對抗<br />\nOnly a coward can hurt a child<br />\n只有懦夫會傷害弱小嘅孩子<br />\nThey give us corruption<br />\n政權帶來腐敗<br />\nWe give them revolution<br />\n我哋就回敬佢一場革命！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n-Winter on Fire: Ukraine&rsquo;s Fight for Freedom"},{"pid":"63dbb24cd6254150f01ab9550078066b154e6e39","tid":1618813,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:30:49.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"fd3c00b4e4540ec5e3a804918dfad0405b5d56a2","tid":1618813,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a9013bf14ccd4ec83a1c061e3105e87d3a8901","tid":1618813,"uid":2870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:35:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"173e9df51ea296e7f4bc09ff2038e8ac33acb9a9","tid":1618813,"uid":115154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:35:27.000Z","msg":"pushhhhhh"},{"pid":"919851e7c13f423cb20523b1a6b01ce27c2a69e2","tid":1618813,"uid":56224,"like":0,"