></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">繞過立法會立法，政府唔會再遵從法律程序處理法律問題，仲講乜法治！！！</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>推晒比所有人睇懶人包！！！！</strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全力反對「蒙面法」！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:27:42.000Z","msg":"【將恐懼變成革命嘅契機】<br />\n緊急法實行在即，人心惶惶係必然，但千祈唔好畀恐懼控制我哋。越係恐懼，就越要無畏，越要冷靜思考。<br />\n<br />\n至於大家一聽到禁蒙面法，都不期然諗起梁天琦三年前嘅嗰番說話&mdash;&mdash;烏克蘭革命誕生於惡法嘅施行。 今日香港政權跟隨烏克蘭政權嘅手段，搏嘅係香港人唔敢好似烏克蘭人咁反抗，只敢「遊行」、「集會」，不敢明言「革命」。<br />\n<br />\n歷史上有惡法促成革命嘅例子，但不代表我哋翹埋雙手革命就會發生。本channel名為《香港革命指南》，就係要大家意識到呢場唔係「運動」、「示威」，而係香港人顛覆極權嘅真正革命。<br />\n<br />\n政權再次向我哋宣戰。香港人，你哋準備好未？<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We are against the police state<br />\n我哋正與警察國家對抗<br />\nOnly a coward can hurt a child<br />\n只有懦夫會傷害弱小嘅孩子<br />\nThey give us corruption<br />\n政權帶來腐敗<br />\nWe give them revolution<br />\n我哋就回敬佢一場革命！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n-Winter on Fire: Ukraine&rsquo;s Fight for Freedom"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5faf67d2a217d77ec83386fcb5bceaff59bf0afe","tid":1618813,"uid":133033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:09:26.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n面對極權 以死相搏<br />\n<br />\n引用得緊急法 佢預咗有激烈嘅反彈<br />\n唔洗大膽預測 我已經知今日死既人係無法估量<br />\n<br />\n因為今日係蒙面法<br />\n聽日就係你望黑警就可被槍決<br />\n後日就係財產充公<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 唔需要啦 緊急法話你知 <br />\n推唔倒呢個政府 你就係支國人<br />\n仲訴求？ 還眼？ 自己親手去拎啦 呢一切"},{"pid":"35a358b5d4e9bff9b31276ddfe3bdd7501b5ef16","tid":1618813,"uid":74182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:11:57.000Z","msg":"全力反對「緊急法」！"},{"pid":"2338fb4c5fc5d710b9ba6b4cf15a6641e3d11831","tid":1618813,"uid":188963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:12:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35fad8b5bbe740dedfdacac40ed141700865c26e","tid":1618813,"uid":279567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:12:55.000Z","msg":"推比屋企人"},{"pid":"d31b10937acbded345cc07bc898fba922f8179b6","tid":1618813,"uid":35090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:13:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9fa76cc7d779d77f9beb0baa2e60af21cbba661f","tid":1618813,"uid":35265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9beaf0993d32b059a6bd2473b72c95035389173","tid":1618813,"uid":223034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:15:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55ad90933f46bae90687f2e5a8713f1a2ced26f6","tid":1618813,"uid":243847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:17:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bb904400ee04ca0f54842675d14857ba22665e9","tid":1618813,"uid":144125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:17:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />緊急法先係重點"},{"pid":"4d89b0503d73a7a8dcc93466c14f978d04809a84","tid":1618813,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:18:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ed93246b872f0abb4f95466b5a7f31df